Package: spatialPointsEditor
Type: Package
Title: Interactive Editor for Spatial Point Coordinates
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Seyed Jalil", "Alavi", email = "geolearnr@gmail.com", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides interactive tools to visualize and correct coordinates 
    of sf POINT objects. Includes a comprehensive Shiny-based editor with 
    map visualization, drag-and-drop functionality, undo/redo capabilities, 
    and modification tracking.
